OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry but cloudy to
OL,6,Fstart the morning. Becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly dull through the day as
OL,8,Frain spreads east through the
OL,9,Fafternoon, perhaps heavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy through the evening
OL,12,Fwith mainly light rain, heavier and
OL,13,Fmore persistent at times. Staying
OL,14,Fcloudy overnight with rain turning
OL,15,Flighter and more patchy. Remaining
OL,16,Fmainly dry in the southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
