OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FIt will be cloudy and
OL,6,Flargely dry throughout the day, but a
OL,7,Ffew spots of light rain possible here
OL,8,Fand there, most likely in the north
OL,9,Fand west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,13,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter periods too,
OL,15,Fespecially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
